Interface DoFn.RequiresWindowAccess

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AssignWindowsDoFn
    Enclosing class:
    DoFn<InputT,OutputT>

    @Experimental
public static interface DoFn.RequiresWindowAccess
    Interface for signaling that a DoFn needs to access the window the element is being processed in, via DoFn.ProcessContext.window().
